<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jacquard+12&family=Jersey+10&display=swap" 
    rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Manju's Realm</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="nav-container">
            <a class="nav-text" href="/">Manju's Realm</a>
            <a class="nav-text about" href="/blog">Blog</a>
            <a class="nav-text about" href="/about">About</a>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="grid">
        <div class="welcome-container">
            <h2 class="welcome">I’m Manju, and You just stumbled into my Realm. Welcome!</h1>
            <h3 class="welcome">I always dreamed of having my own little part of the Web. Here, I can share whatever I want to the world! Please enjoy your stay, You can look at what my current and past interests, any projects that I may be working on, and my blog! Then, if you wish to say anything to Me, send me an e-mail! I’ll be sure to reply.</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="status-container"></div>
        <div class="blog-container">

            <h1 class="latest">Latest Post</h1>

            <h2 class="post-title"><%- latest_post.title -%></h2>

            <div class="post-body"><%- latest_post.content -%></div>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>